channel.description:
Hello. A few days ago i had an idea to make a godwars dungeon. And i want it to look really cool. So im putting together a team, so we can make an awesome Godwars Dungeon. So.... lets start. Application:
What role would you like to be? Whats your experience with that role? Do you think that you will be a good help?
Roles: Client Help: Green U --------- --------- Coders: X-J-K-X --------- Testers:No More Are Needed At The Moment. All Application Will Be Denied For Tester. dantotman Thedup Website/Fourm Creators: --------- --------- Update:None at the moment. If i have forgotten a role or anything else please contact me by Private Message or my msn. MSN:SockScape@hotmail.com Thanks To All!
